author: RNG
title: Words as Well as Elections Have Consequences
text: Words as Well as Elections Have Consequences I guess the rank and file really don't like truth. Quote: Originally Posted by CNN email House Majority Leader Kevin McCarthy has dropped out of the race to succeed retiring Speaker John Boehner, House Republicans say. The shocking move came without warning as House Republicans were in a closed-door meeting to select their nominee for speaker. Boehner has also postponed internal leadership elections that were supposed to start on Thursday. Get complete coverage of breaking news on CNN TV, CNN.com and CNN Mobile.
